{"tid":819970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"先達店預測 iPhone XS Max 炒高五千港元","createTime":"2018-09-15T07:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T12:59:44.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"701a1b2e7de8b0ba0bb082b84fedf5668d515cb2","tid":819970,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T07:24:35.000Z","msg":"iPhone XR、XS、XS Max 推出，「果農」最關心嘅一定係有無得炒。去年 iPhone X 推出時，有預測可炒上 2 萬、3 萬、甚至 10 萬！不過最終未有實現。今次 Apple 發布 iPhone XR、XS、XS Max，<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=%2FJ%2FZ3zBmxpWOjrIK420EkgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=295f5c88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 同大家計過，大陸定價比香港最多貴近 HK$2,000【新 iPhone 定價按此】，究竟會唔會掀起炒風？小記就搵來幾位先達打滾多年的炒家，跟大家分享對 iPhone XR、XS、XS Max 嘅「投機」意見。<br />\n<br />\niPhone XS Max 512GB 有機會炒得起，因採用 6.5 吋全新規格，又有 512GB 版兼雙卡雙待，預期炒高 HK$2,000 至 HK$3,000，但不會維持太耐；iPhone XS 不建議「沾手」，可能比原價低 HK$400 至 HK$500。至於同屬新尺寸的 iPhone XR，阿勇認為或可吸引不少用戶換機，尤其是女生，應該幾搶手，惟炒價有限，應只有 HK$500 至 HK$800 水位。<br />\n<br />\n萬通 Ricky：炒高 HK$5,000！<br />\n<br />\nRicky 睇好 iPhone XS Max 512GB，預期首批有機會炒高 HK$4,000 至 HK$5,000；iPhone XR 128GB 有機會炒高 HK$2,000，但預計炒價頂多維持 1 個月，視乎蘋果出貨量是否足夠，又估計 64GB 的入門型號會海量供貨，可能極速跌破「招股價」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2155000/2159809/iPhone_XS_Max_SinTat_Estimate_Price_03_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2155000%2F2159809%2FiPhone_XS_Max_SinTat_Estimate_Price_03_600.jpeg&h=050bdbf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萬通首席策略分析師睇好iPhone炒高5000元"},{"pid":"cd234428494e9f2d2c20d352a80822432f01c36f","tid":819970,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T07:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e89ac1d6b37c8e91ba3f7f243dc530e04bfb4b6","tid":819970,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-1